The detective is part of the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force and mentions coordinating with a prosecutor and an FBI Special Agent partner.

keyFacts: The correspondence involves scheduling a video interview for an investigation related to child exploitation and human trafficking.
The detective is a member of the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force, indicating a joint federal-local investigation.
An FBI Special Agent is explicitly named as a partner in the investigation.
The interview was initially set for January 5, 2021, but was canceled and a reschedule to the week of January 26, 2021, is proposed.
